This paper deals with image processing and regularization techniques, which are typically studied in the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.MM) communities. The paper also involves mathematical analysis of norms and subdifferentials, which falls under the categories of information theory (cs.IT), machine learning (cs.LG), and numerical analysis (cs.NA).
